column6: Venom and his band of mighty monsters take the fight to the Spider-Queen once and for all! This time, though, he's not going it alone - he'll have a webslinging wonder by his side! PLUS! Don't miss the conclusion to the return of the one and only MAYDAY PARKER as Spider-Woman by DeFalco, Frenz, Buscema and Crossley!
